The files contained in this folder are designed to work on a large number of
large and huge files in an asynchronous fashion.

FFProbeDispatcher:      ffd
FFProbeAnalyzer:        ffa
CallBackEventHandler:   cbh
  ---------------       -------
  | ffd  :  cbh |       | ffa |
  ---------------       -------
     |       |             |
    | |      |             |
    | |------+----------->| |
     |       |            | |
     |      | |<----------| |
    | |<--- | |            |
     |       |             |

The problem of analyzing disjunctive large data quantities have been solved by
using parallel computation, leaving the DOMS-injection up to the originating
class.

